query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('acid-base',
'inorganic-chemistry',
'organic-chemistry',
'thermodynamics')
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('chemistry') group by t1.name;
